					<h1> 2 重生</h1>
					<div class="bottem1">
						<a href="javascript:;" onclick="showpop('/modules/article/uservote.php?id=10848&amp;ajax_request=1');">投推荐票</a> <a href="/shu10848/index.html">上一章</a> ← <a href="http://www.qushuba.com/shu10848/">章节目录</a> → <a href="/shu10848/6329631.html">下一章</a> <a href="javascript:;" onclick="showpop('/modules/article/addbookcase.php?id=10848&amp;cid=6329630&amp;ajax_request=1');">加入书签</a>
